(40, 'wc-admin-add-first-product-note', 'email', 'en_US', 'Add your first product', '{greetings}<br /><br />Nice one; you\'ve created a WooCommerce store! Now it\'s time to add your first product and get ready to start selling.<br /><br />There are three ways to add your products: you can <strong>create products manually, import them at once via CSV file</strong>, or <strong>migrate them from another service</strong>.<br /><br /><a href=\"https://docs.woocommerce.com/document/managing-products/?utm_source=help_panel&amp;utm_medium=product\">Explore our docs</a> for more information, or just get started!', '{\"role\":\"administrator\"}', 'unactioned', 'woocommerce-admin', '2021-10-30 13:51:05', NULL, 0, 'plain', 'https://createwise.cryptogallery.space/wp-content/plugins/woocommerce/packages/woocommerce-admin/images/admin_notes/dashboard-widget-setup.png', 0, 'info', 0),
